name: "Dead Bunny" by Sunny Crittenden
description: In May 2012, this bunny got into our fenced yard to have a feast in the veggie garden & didn't find its way out to avoid my dogs being let out early in the morning. The dogs ran around, barking & chasing the bunny relentlessly, until the bunny ran out of batteries, collapsed & died. The second the bunny was lifeless, the dogs stopped caring. This photo often describes how I feel because I run myself ragged until I burn out, become exhausted, and physically & emotionally canâ€™t do any more.
